Photos : China ' s Sichuan province rocked by powerful earthquake - Ottawa Citizen Ottawa Citizen - ‎ 44 minutes ago ‎ A powerful earthquake rocked southwest China ' s Sihchuan province , striking close to the city of Ya ' an on the edge of the Tibetan Plateau just after 8 : 00 am , setting off landslides , destroying buildings and triggering a major rescue operation on April 20 , 2013 .